- Grandma says you went crazy.

03:34.510 --> 03:35.510
- [Grandma] Bridget!

03:39.720 --> 03:41.570
- Well, yeah, I basically went crazy.

03:48.320 --> 03:49.470
- You don't seem crazy.

04:02.313 --> 04:04.563
- I need to check my phone.

04:16.858 --> 04:19.526
(ominous music)

04:24.734 --> 04:26.658
(metallic clattering)

04:26.658 --> 04:28.908
(growling)

04:33.689 --> 04:36.439
(water dripping)

04:41.667 --> 04:45.207
(metallic clattering)

04:45.207 --> 04:47.457
(growling)

04:53.521 --> 04:56.521
(crickets chirping)

05:28.657 --> 05:31.324
(intense music)

06:01.098 --> 06:06.098
("Girls Just Wanna Have
Fun" by Cyndi Lauper)

06:16.339 --> 06:18.362
♪ I come home in the morning light ♪

06:18.362 --> 06:22.002
♪ My mother says, when you
gonna live your life right ♪

